al <del>5萬5</del>一年?</blockquote><br />\n4萬5一年?</blockquote><br />\n4-5千學費一年，一星期五堂每堂兩個鐘，一般有三十人左右，咩年紀/段位/國籍都有，大半係住日本既外國人，所以宿舍比夠少人！學費同住宿都好平！真心弘揚柔道既殿堂！"},{"pid":"9f1292cfcb94e62a5c2679c4add005e25ce76094","tid":449144,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係大阪?</blockquote><br />\n我去左東京，係巨蛋隔離！"},{"pid":"9519d54c82c4eab4c6c4559ca231c4f7fa6d5c63","tid":449144,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係大阪?</blockquote><br />\n我去左東京，係巨蛋隔離！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/142324_f35d7b0baab4e006e2b8532e123107ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F142324_f35d7b0baab4e006e2b8532e123107ae.jpg&h=b3a09631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/142326_fa7096d59b6887177d9ca03b5a22d1bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F142326_fa7096d59b6887177d9ca03b5a22d1bf.jpg&h=01bfd3c9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}